  <entry>
    <title>[Success] 2023 - Mt.WuGong Trail 武功山反穿</title>
    <url>/2023/06/09/%5BSuccess%5D%202023%20-%20Mt.WuGong%20Trail%20%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9F%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%8D%E7%A9%BF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>简单介绍一下本次路线，3天2晚，从龙山村反穿武功山</p>
<h2 id="Day1-周五-晚-🚄-上海-萍乡"><a href="#Day1-周五-晚-🚄-上海-萍乡" class="headerlink" title="Day1 周五 晚 🚄 上海 - 萍乡"></a>Day1 周五 晚 🚄 上海 - 萍乡</h2><p>周五下班，直冲上海南站</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6359.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>我的小鹰，算算也快10年了，橡皮筋都松了但感觉将就将就还能用（主要是没钱，现在登山包都好贵啊，苍穹也好，穿岳也好都要2000+，啧啧啧）</p>
<p>不过，看着确实有点旧了，要不要换呢 🤔️</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6360.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>到早了，等了1个小时，检票上车</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6361.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>好久好久没坐绿皮硬卧车了，一点点兴奋</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6363.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>车上全是“特种兵”，全是下了班去武功山徒步的上班族，上班族哦，还不是大学生大军。</p>
<p>车上听着旁边人闲聊，好些个都是网友见面，之前彼此都是不认识的，真心佩服这些e人，自来熟的特别快，然后，有妹子的地方，就有男生装逼，哎，没啥意思 。</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6364.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6365.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<hr>
<h2 id="Day-2-萍乡站-龙山村-发云界-好汉坡-绝望坡-观音宕"><a href="#Day-2-萍乡站-龙山村-发云界-好汉坡-绝望坡-观音宕" class="headerlink" title="Day 2 萍乡站 - 龙山村 - 发云界 - 好汉坡 - 绝望坡 - 观音宕"></a>Day 2 萍乡站 - 龙山村 - 发云界 - 好汉坡 - 绝望坡 - 观音宕</h2><p>早上7点到萍乡站，满满当当全是登山包，人也精神了许多，像不像要去打仗。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6369.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>人，有多少呢，你看去徒步入口龙王村的车都堵住了，下来徒步进山。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6370.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<table><tbody><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6371.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6372.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<p>一开始的路竹林密布，郁郁葱葱，感觉还不错，体感也不是很热</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6373.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>001号路标，之前在香港徒步麦理浩径时还特别羡慕500米有个路标的，现在看看大陆这块其实也在提升，赞。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6374.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>武功山徒步是一条非常非常成熟的路线，有多成熟呢，小卖部有卖西瓜🍉，按片卖，真是大开眼界，爬完一个坡，大家都坐下来喝水补给，小卖部生意红火的不行，老板还在那里凡尔赛，说就周末两天人多，赚个小钱，切～</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6375.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6376.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6377.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>穿出竹林，豁然开朗，武功山的绿扑面而来</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6378.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6379.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<table><tbody><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6380.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6381.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<p>没有滤镜，6月份，武功山的草，就是这么绿</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6384.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6393.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6390.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>到达第一个观景台，发云界，第一面红旗🚩出现了。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6394.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6395.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>在发云界的民宿吃了一口粉，说实话，并，不好吃。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6396.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6397.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<table><tbody><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6401.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6404.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6407.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6409.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<p>绝望坡来了，</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6410.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<table><tbody><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6412.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6413.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<p>过了观音宕，天色渐暗，山顶全是景区运营搭的帐篷，甚至还有个舞台和一个小的足球场</p>
<p>个人感觉，虽然方便了游客来观光露营，但对生态环境真的是造成了挺大破坏，而且，有点流氓…竭尽所能用帐篷占着最好的地块，哎。</p>
<p>往前又走了几百米，找了相对平缓的平台，虽然风很大，但正对东方，明天日出应该很不错。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6415.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<h2 id="Day-3-观音宕-吊马桩-金顶-下山-上海"><a href="#Day-3-观音宕-吊马桩-金顶-下山-上海" class="headerlink" title="Day 3 观音宕 - 吊马桩 - 金顶 - 下山 - 上海"></a>Day 3 观音宕 - 吊马桩 - 金顶 - 下山 - 上海</h2><p>晚上睡的一般，主要旁边又扎了两个帐篷，有一点点吵，哎</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6418.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>日出，有一说一，我这个露营的位置，是真的很赞，正对日出，前方没有遮挡</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6420.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>哇，看如此美景，所有疲劳都值得了</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6423.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6425.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>嘻嘻，看简介，我看了半天，没看出来 啊哈哈哈⬇️</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6430.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>到了，武功山金顶，每晚都有好多大学生在这边挥舞红旗🇨🇳，非常狂热，怎么说呢，就，很文革….</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6432.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>看完金顶，准备下山，心想着坐索道舒舒服服，优雅下山，但是，没想到，排队人是如此之多，说好的特种兵呢？</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6435.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>武功山有两级索道，一个金顶索道，一个中庵索道，金顶索道要排1个半小时，行，那我走到中庵再坐，等我走到中庵，这边要排3小时，阿西吧，为了赶上高铁，咬着牙往山下走。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6438.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>人人人人人人人人人人人人人</p>
<table><tbody><tr><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6439.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td><td><img    
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://img.ureylou.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6440.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                         alt=""
                 ></td></tr></tbody></table>

<p>经历千辛万苦，左膝又有点抽筋的感觉，看来上次香港的伤还没好透，好在一路补给点很多，可以及时的补充水份和能量</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6443.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>反穿成功，留影打卡武功山。</p>
<p>每次爬完山，站在山脚下，看着自己征服过的山峰⛰️，自豪感油然而生。</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_6445.jpeg?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
<p>没想到，强度还是挺大的，2天重装，累计爬升2388m，看来我还是很强壮的嘛，💪💪💪</p>
<p><img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="https://ureylou-blog.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/2023-China-Mt.WuGong/IMG_7283.PNG?x-oss-process=style/view"
                       
                 ></p>
]]></content>
